WEBVTT

00:04:56.080 --> 00:05:02.160
The method we adopted for learning
is not a fool-proof studying method.

00:05:02.680 --> 00:05:08.256
This journey was full
of difficulties for us,

00:05:08.280 --> 00:05:13.596
but by encouraging my girls
to follow this path,

00:05:13.596 --> 00:05:17.946
I made a noble attempt
in making them realize

00:05:17.946 --> 00:05:22.870
that learning can also be
a source of happiness.

00:05:23.001 --> 00:05:25.071
(Applause)

00:05:26.480 --> 00:05:31.056
During home schooling, whatever
Malvika and Radha learnted